--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 364c2b772391e46dba637935c558b9b2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Fortress
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MythSO
  pageNumber: 127
  mythName: Fortress
  omens:
  - '1. The Thorn Seer roams the Realm,

    proclaiming an invasion of great scuttling

    monsters
    is coming soon.'
  - '2. A messenger declares that the Thorn Seer

    has reclaimed a lost fortress
    (in the Myth

    Hex), creating an impenetrable sanctuary

    for when the
    invasion comes.'
  - '3. Three claw swarm cutters peer from their

    tunnels, scouts for the invasion.
    If seen

    they scutter back underground.'
  - '4. A smith and her three young apprentices

    are looking for a new home.
    They left the

    Fortress, as the Thorn Seer wanted the

    impossible from
    them, demanding whole

    walls of iron be built.'
  - '5. The voice of the Thorn Seer is heard

    across the land. The invasion is
    here,

    numberless hordes of the claw swarm

    attacking the Fortress. They
    will not

    actually breach the Fortress, as they are

    creations of the
    Thorn Seer.'
  - '6. The invasion defeated, the Thorn Seer

    demands to be made ruler of the
    Realm,

    the Fortress as his Seat of Power.'
  verse: 'A cage in stone, all thorned and vast

    Disguise a scheme in shadows
    cast'
  castEntries:
  - name: The Thorn Seer
    statBlock: 'VIG 9, CLA 16, SPI 14, 3 GD

      A2 (thorny body, helm)'
    notes: 'Spined mace (d8 hefty), dagger (d6)

      Sees pain in the past and
      the future.'
  - name: Claw Swarm Cutter
    statBlock: 'VIG 9, CLA 9, SPI 3, 3 GD

      A1 (green carapace)'
    notes: 'Claws (2d6), acid spit (d8)

      Cunning instinct (see below).'
  - name: Claw Swarm Hulk
    statBlock: 'VIG 15, CLA 5, SPI 5, 6 GD

      A2 (red carapace)'
    notes: Great claws (2d8), blunt instinct
  flavorTable:
    title: CUNNING INSTINCTS
    columns:
    - header: Action
      values:
      - Burrow
      - Scatter
      - Camouflage
      - Sprout wings
      - Spawn more
      - Spit acid
    - header: Objective
      values:
      - Regroup later
      - Surprise the enemy
      - Target a single enemy
      - Confuse the enemy
      - Set up an advantage
      - Exploit a weak spot
  visibleByDefault: 0
  visibleMarkerPrefab: {fileID: 0}
